author: Wochit
title: Some Trump companies owe thousands in back taxes
text: Some Trump companies owe thousands in back taxes In January, the New York Department of State issued a warrant against Ivanka Trump's business, called "Ivanka Trump Fine Jewelry," for more than five thousand dollars in unpaid taxes.
